<br/><br/>

<p>My next task is to replace the pins with meaningful icons. I've been <a href=".../image/logo/">collecing logos</a>. I think watching 
<object data=".../image/logo/McDonald's/" type="image/svg+xml" class="letter">
<a href=".../image/logo/McDonanld's">McDonald's</a>
</object>s
and 
<object data=".../image/logo/Wal-mart/button" type="image/svg+xml" class="letter">
<a href=".../image/logo/Wal-mart">Wal-mart</a>
</object>s
march across the world would be interesting.</p>

<p>Where I'd like to go with this eventually is a visual history of the Earth. Show different types of dinosaurs roaming around during the periods they existed. I think it would help people get a better sense of what it means that 6000 years of recorded history is 0.001% of the 570 million years of life on the planet. 0.001% of 6000 years is 22 days.</p>

